0. Allow user to select their default (known) language
1. Allow user to search a song (or provide go-to songs) 
2. Query Genius API to get the song id 
3. Query Genius Song Lyrics API with the song id
4. Retrieve the html of the lyrics in response
5. Clean the html (be mindful of the unicodes)
6. Display the lyrics
    7. Query Google Translate API of each line of lyrics in user's default language
    8. Display translated lyrics next to/underneath the original lyrics